item.content:encoded: Wonderful photo essay on Disneyland's Tomorrowland and the changes the place has gone through. I visited Disneyland in July of 2003, it was our second time (we had visited in 2001) and it wasn't the magical place we used to see on the TV. It was a bit run down, in need of some serious love and care. (Link courtesy of Screamscape)
